{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/spring-restapi-04.md/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"mysql-설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mysql-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"mysql 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MySQL 설치하기</h3>\n<p>Spring에서 MySQL을 사용하기 위해 먼저 MySQL의 설치가 필요하다.<br></p>\n<p>MySQL 다운로드 : <a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/</a></p>\n<p>자신의 OS에 맞는 버전을 설치하면 된다.</p>\n<p>이때 root의 패스워드를 정하게 되는데, 절대 잊어먹지말고 기억해두자. (매모장에 저장해 놓는게 좋다.)</p>\n<p>설치가 다 됐다면 터미널을 열어 <code class=\"language-text\">Mysql -u root -p</code>를 입력해보자.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 587px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b34e092dca515836b6c82f1bb69d4f8f/d72eb/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.37837837837837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/b34e092dca515836b6c82f1bb69d4f8f/d72eb/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b34e092dca515836b6c82f1bb69d4f8f/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/b34e092dca515836b6c82f1bb69d4f8f/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/b34e092dca515836b6c82f1bb69d4f8f/d72eb/5.png 587w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위와 같이 Mysql에 연결이 된다면 설치 완료.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<h3 id=\"database-gui에-대해서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#database-gui%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"database gui에 대해서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DataBase GUI에 대해서</h3>\n<p>DataBase를 구축할 때 여러 편의기능을 사용하기 위해 GUI툴을 사용하곤한다.<br>\nMysql의 대표적인 GUI툴로는 MysqlWorkbench가 있다.</p>\n<p>MySQL Workbench 다운로드 : <a href=\"https://www.mysql.com/products/workbench/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.mysql.com/products/workbench/</a></p>\n<p>같은 회사에서 만들었으니 가장 최적화가 잘 돼있을 것이다.<br>\n하지만 MySQL Workbench는 맥북 M1칩과 호환되지 않는다...</p>\n<p>정말 많은 GUI툴들이 있지만 아직 학생이라면 Intellij의 Data Grip을 추천한다.</p>\n<p>Data Grip 다운로드 : <a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/ko-kr/datagrip/download/#section=mac\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.jetbrains.com/ko-kr/datagrip/download/#section=mac</a>\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<h3 id=\"mvn-repository\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mvn-repository\" aria-label=\"mvn repository permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MVN Repository</h3>\n<p>Spring에서 Mysql를 사용하기 위해서 2가지의 Dependency를 추가해줘야한다.</p>\n<p>Mysql Connection / J : <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/mysql/mysql-connector-java\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/mysql/mysql-connector-java</a>\n<br>\nMybatis Spring Boot Starter : <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.mybatis.spring.boot/mybatis-spring-boot-starter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.mybatis.spring.boot/mybatis-spring-boot-starter</a></p>\n<p>Mysql Connection / J는 java에서 Mysql을 연결하기 위한 드라이버를 의미하고,<br>\nMybatis Spring Boot Starter는 Database와 관련된 복잡한 세팅들을 자동으로 해주는 드라이버를 의미한다.</p>\n<p>Mybatis 덕분에 Mapper를 사용할 수 있는 것이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/mysql/mysql-connector-java --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dependency</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>mysql<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>mysql-connector-java<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- &lt;version>8.0.23&lt;/version> --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dependency</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.mybatis.spring.boot/mybatis-spring-boot-starter --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dependency</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>org.mybatis.spring.boot<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>mybatis-spring-boot-starter<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>2.1.4<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dependency</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>두 dependency를 Spring 프로젝트의 pom.xml 파일의 dependencies 아래에 추가해준다.</p>\n<p>이때 버전 부분은 Spring이 자동으로 Spring 자신의 버전과 잘 맞는 버전을 설치하기 때문에 지워주는 것이 좋다.</p>\n<p>그리고 application.properties 파일에서 database의 정보를 작성해주면 연결은 끝이난다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/&lt;Database Name&gt;?useUnicode=ture&amp;characterEncoding=utf8&amp;serverTimezone=Asia/Seoul\nspring.datasource.username=root\nspring.datasource.password=&lt;password&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같이 3줄을 작성해주면 되는데, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Database Name&gt;</code> 에는 연결할 DB명, 즉 스키마 명을 넣어주면된다.<br>\n그리고 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;password&gt;</code>에는 Mysql 설치시 입력했던 root의 패스워드를 넣어주면 된다.</p>\n<p><b>※ DB를 생성하고 그 안에 table을 생성할 때, 기존에 선언한 Spring Model 객체와 이름이 똑같아야한다. (대소문자는 구분하지 않는다.)</b>\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<h3 id=\"mapper\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mapper\" aria-label=\"mapper permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mapper</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/29114/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/fcda8/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/12f09/3.png 148w,\n/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\n/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/fcda8/3.png 590w,\n/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/efc66/3.png 885w,\n/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/c83ae/3.png 1180w,\n/static/0868b65c1c121fd7586549f15b689c2d/29114/3.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Controller 패키지, Model 패키지와 같은 위치에 Mapper 패키지를 생성해주고 그 안에 Interface를 생성해준다.</p>\n<p>그리고 위와 같이 작성해 주면 되는데 마찬가지로 어노테이션으로 Mapper임을 선언해주면 된다.</p>\n<p>예시 테스트를 위해 Select문을 하나 작성해주는데, 어노테이션으로 Select문임을 인지해주고 괄호안에 sql문을 작성해주면 된다. 그리고 아래 해당 sql문을 실행시킬 함수를 작성해준다.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<h3 id=\"controller\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#controller\" aria-label=\"controller permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Controller</h3>\n<p>마지막으로 Controller에서 Mapper의 함수를 호출해주기만 하면 된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/29114/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/fcda8/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/fcda8/4.png 590w,\n/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/efc66/4.png 885w,\n/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/c83ae/4.png 1180w,\n/static/4e3c8b7ce545605c12e8c200b442f2db/29114/4.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n(주석 참고)</p>\n<p>결론적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">/user/all</code>를 호출하게 되면 <code class=\"language-text\">mapper.getStudyModel</code>을 호출하게 되고, 그럼 mapper의 sql문을 실행하게 돼 그 값이 최종적으로 리턴된다.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<h3 id=\"결과물\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC%EB%AC%BC\" aria-label=\"결과물 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결과물</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/d74fe/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.27027027027026%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/fcda8/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/12f09/6.png 148w,\n/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\n/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/fcda8/6.png 590w,\n/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/efc66/6.png 885w,\n/static/b474ff2cb718ecb8d6066d1ce7631f04/d74fe/6.png 1164w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>DB에 test값을 넣은 후 주소를 호출하면 잘 불러와지는 것을 볼 수 있다.</p>","excerpt":"MySQL 설치하기 Spring에서 MySQL을 사용하기 위해 먼저 MySQL의 설치가 필요하다. MySQL 다운로드 : https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/ 자신의 OS에 맞는 버전을 설치하면 된다. 이때 root의…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-04.md/#mysql-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">MySQL 설치하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-04.md/#database-gui%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C\">DataBase GUI에 대해서</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-04.md/#mvn-repository\">MVN Repository</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-04.md/#mapper\">Mapper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-04.md/#controller\">Controller</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-04.md/#%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC%EB%AC%BC\">결과물</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/spring-restapi-04.md/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring을 통한 REST API 예제 - 04","date":"Mar 26, 2021","tags":["Springboot"],"keywords":["MojitoBar","Ju dongseok"],"update":"Mar 26, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/spring-restapi-04.md/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-03-26"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}